## Sample local.properties (copy to local.properties — never commit secrets)

# Android SDK (required)
# sdk.dir=F:\\AndroidSDK

# Simple Telemetry MVP — must match viwa-telemetry MACHINE_ENROLLMENT_KEY (.env)
# See docs/SIMPLE_TELEMETRY_MVP_ANDROID.md and viwa-telemetry/.env.example
# telemetry.enrollmentKey=your-dev-enrollment-key-here

# Alternative: set env VIWA_TELEMETRY_ENROLLMENT_KEY before gradlew (PowerShell: $env:VIWA_TELEMETRY_ENROLLMENT_KEY = "...")
